1. It was made into a DoT<br>
2. Damage was capped<br>
3. Crits gone<br>
4. 1 minute interval<br>
5. was aggro increased?<br>
<br>
So now it seems that 6 *SIX* rangers have killed Sontalak... will they be nerfed, will you laugh, or will you cry?<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fprexus81531frm7.showMessage?topicID=2443.topic">pub140.ezboard.com/fprexu...2443.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
