<br>
Yes, Kunark dragons can now be killed by 6 or less of any class or combination of classes, but SOE isn’t worked up about it because there is still a more than minimal risk….for example, 4 of those 6 rangers died before Sontalak was finally killed.<br>
<br>
However, as many posters have wished, it would be nice if they gave us back the crits (other than innate) and possibly lowered the refresh timer a bit, while keeping the &quot;one per minute&quot; restriction.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=natanmagus>Natan Magus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 1004<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/10/03 11:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> re:</span><hr size=1> {quote]Stuff like Carprin - Highpriest cycle would have been totally trivialized by manaburn.[/qoute]<br>
