<br>
As it is now MB is allmost an insult to a PoP level 65 Wizard. And a waste - a placeholder - for a good AA skill.<br>
<br>
Heh, SKs even can HT with their AA disc for over 8.5K. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=oxoxoxoxox>Oxoxo Xoxox</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 1085<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/10/03 11:09 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re:</span><hr size=1> Dont assume that the people that think the Manaburn nerf was idiotic didnt think some adjustment was warranted.<br>
